{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Earth Pig|kanji=己亥|romaji=tsuchinoto i|onyomi=kigai|p=jǐhài|w=chi-hai|mi=t͡ɕi³⁵ xaɪ̯|y=gei2 hoi6|j=gei2 hoi6|ci=kei hɐi|mc=kɨj ɣəi|oc-bs=kɯʔ ɢəʔ}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive}} '''Yin Earth Pig''', also known as '''Kigai''' (己亥, Tsuchinoto-i, Kidonoinoshishi, Kigai), is one of the elements in the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
It is the 36th combination in the Sexagenary cycle, following {{ill|Wu Xu|ja|戊戌|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and preceding {{ill|Geng Zi|ja|庚子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. According to {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Ji|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Earth (Wu Xing)|ja|土|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branch|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Hai|ja|亥|1=Pig (zodiac)|lt=Pig (亥)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Water (Wu Xing)|ja|水|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, creating a {{ill|Five Elements#Mutual overcoming|ja|相剋|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Earth overcomes Water) relationship.
== Years of the Yin Earth Pig == Years in which the remainder when divided by 60 is 39 are considered Yin Earth Pig years.
{| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of the Yin Earth Pig''' |- ![[1st millennium]]!![[2nd millennium]]!![[3rd millennium]] |- | * [[39]] * [[99]] * [[159]] * [[219]] * [[279]] * [[339]] * [[399]] * [[459]] * [[519]] * [[579]] * [[639]] * [[699]] * [[759]] * [[819]] * [[879]] * [[939]] * [[999]] | * [[1059]] * [[1119]] * [[1179]] * [[1239]] * [[1299]] * [[1359]] * [[1419]] * [[1479]] * [[1539]] * [[1599]] * [[1659]] * [[1719]] * [[1779]] * [[1839]] * [[1899]] * [[1959]] | * [[2019]] * [[2079]] * [[2139]] * [[2199]] * [[2259]] * [[2319]] * [[2379]] * [[2439]] * [[2499]] * [[2559]] * [[2619]] * [[2679]] * [[2739]] * [[2799]] * [[2859]] * [[2919]] * [[2979]] |}
== Months of the Yin Earth Pig == In years where the last digit is 1 or 6 (corresponding to the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}), the {{ill|October|ja|10月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of that year is considered a Yin Earth Pig month. However, this applies to the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, and in some cases, the {{ill|Solar terms|ja|節月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (from {{ill|Lidong|ja|立冬|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to the day before {{ill|Daxue|ja|大雪|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) is used.
== Days of the Yin Earth Pig == === Selection Days === Yin Earth Pig days are the 7th day of the {{ill|Ten'ichi Tenjō|ja|天一天上|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} cycle.
