It is the 36th combination in the Sexagenary cycle, following {{ill|Wu Xu|ja|戊戌|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and preceding {{ill|Geng Zi|ja|庚子|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. According to {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|Ji|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Earth (Wu Xing)|ja|土|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branch|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|Hai|ja|亥|1=Pig (zodiac)|lt=Pig (亥)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Water (Wu Xing)|ja|水|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, creating a {{ill|Five Elements#Mutual overcoming|ja|相剋|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (Earth overcomes Water) relationship.
== Years of the Yin Earth Pig == Years in which the remainder when divided by 60 is 39 are considered Yin Earth Pig years.
{| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of the Yin Earth Pig''' |- ![[1st millennium]]!![[2nd millennium]]!![[3rd millennium]] |- | * [[39]] * [[99]] * [[159]] * [[219]] * [[279]] * [[339]] * [[399]] * [[459]] * [[519]] * [[579]] * [[639]] * [[699]] * [[759]] * [[819]] * [[879]] * [[939]] * [[999]] | * [[1059]] * [[1119]] * [[1179]] * [[1239]] * [[1299]] * [[1359]] * [[1419]] * [[1479]] * [[1539]] * [[1599]] * [[1659]] * [[1719]] * [[1779]] * [[1839]] * [[1899]] * [[1959]] | * [[2019]] * [[2079]] * [[2139]] * [[2199]] * [[2259]] * [[2319]] * [[2379]] * [[2439]] * [[2499]] * [[2559]] * [[2619]] * [[2679]] * [[2739]] * [[2799]] * [[2859]] * [[2919]] * [[2979]] |}
== Months of the Yin Earth Pig == In years where the last digit is 1 or 6 (corresponding to the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}), the {{ill|October|ja|10月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} of that year is considered a Yin Earth Pig month. However, this applies to the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, and in some cases, the {{ill|Solar terms|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (from {{ill|Lidong|ja|立冬|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Daxue|ja|大雪|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}) is used.
== Days of the Yin Earth Pig == === Selection Days === Yin Earth Pig days are the 7th day of the {{ill|Ten'ichi Tenjō|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} cycle.
