{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Earth Pig|kanji=己亥|romaji=tsuchinoto i|onyomi=kigai|p=jǐhài|w=chi-hai|mi=t͡ɕi³⁵ xaɪ̯|y=gei2 hoi6|j=gei2 hoi6|ci=kei hɐi|mc=kɨj ɣəi|oc-bs=kɯʔ ɢəʔ|qq=}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}} '''Yin Earth Pig''', also known as '''Kigai''' (己亥, Tsuchinoto-i, Kidonoinoshishi, Kigai), is one of the elements in the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.
It is the 36th combination in the Sexagenary cycle, following {{ill|Wu Xu|ja|1=Yang Earth Dog|2=ja|戊戌|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wu Xu|qq=}} and preceding {{ill|Geng Zi|ja|1=Yang Metal Rat|2=ja|庚子|1=Yang Metal Rat|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Geng Zi|qq=}}. According to {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=}} {{ill|Ji|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ji|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Earth (Wu Xing)|ja|土|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth (Wu Xing)|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branch|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branch|qq=}} {{ill|Hai|ja|亥|1=Pig (zodiac)|lt=Pig (亥)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hai|13=User:Immanuelle/Pig (zodiac)|qq=}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Water (Wu Xing)|ja|水|1=Water (wuxing)|lt=Water (水)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water (Wu Xing)|qq=}}, creating a {{ill|Five Elements#Mutual overcoming|ja|相剋|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Five Elements#Mutual overcoming|qq=}} (Earth overcomes Water) relationship.
