ft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Five Elements#Mutual overcoming|qq=}} (Earth overcomes Water) relationship.
== Years of the Yin Earth Pig == Years in which the remainder when divided by 60 is 39 are considered Yin Earth Pig years.
{| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of the Yin Earth Pig''' |- ![[1st millennium]]!![[2nd millennium]]!![[3rd millennium]] |- | * [[39]] * [[99]] * [[159]] * [[219]] * [[279]] * [[339]] * [[399]] * [[459]] * [[519]] * [[579]] * [[639]] * [[699]] * [[759]] * [[819]] * [[879]] * [[939]] * [[999]] | * [[1059]] * [[1119]] * [[1179]] * [[1239]] * [[1299]] * [[1359]] * [[1419]] * [[1479]] * [[1539]] * [[1599]] * [[1659]] * [[1719]] * [[1779]] * [[1839]] * [[1899]] * [[1959]] | * [[2019]] * [[2079]] * [[2139]] * [[2199]] * [[2259]] * [[2319]] * [[2379]] * [[2439]] * [[2499]] * [[2559]] * [[2619]] * [[2679]] * [[2739]] * [[2799]] * [[2859]] * [[2919]] * [[2979]] |}
== Months of the Yin Earth Pig == In years where the last digit is 1 or 6 (corresponding to the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=}} {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|lt=Kanoto (辛)|2=ja|3=辛|4=zh|5=辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|lt=Hinoe (丙)|2=ja|3=丙|4=zh|5=丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=}}), the {{ill|October|ja|10月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October|qq=}} of that year is considered a Yin Earth Pig month. However, this applies to the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}, and in some cases, the {{ill|Solar terms|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar terms|qq=}} (from {{ill|Lidong|ja|立冬|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lidong|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Daxue|ja|大雪|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daxue|qq=}}) is used.
== Days of the Yin Earth Pig == === Selection Days === Yin Earth Pig days are the 7th day of the {{ill|Ten'ichi Tenjō|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten'ichi Tenjō|qq=}} cycle.
