== Months of the Yin Earth Pig == In years where the last digit is 1 or 6 (corresponding to the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=}} {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|lt=Kanoto (辛)|2=ja|3=辛|4=zh|5=辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|lt=Hinoe (丙)|2=ja|3=丙|4=zh|5=丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=}}), the {{ill|October|ja|10月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October|qq=}} of that year is considered a Yin Earth Pig month. However, this applies to the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}, and in some cases, the {{ill|Solar terms|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar terms|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar terms|qq=}} (from {{ill|Lidong|ja|立冬|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lidong|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lidong|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Daxue|ja|大雪|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daxue|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daxue|qq=}}) is used.
== Days of the Yin Earth Pig == === Selection Days === Yin Earth Pig days are the 7th day of the {{ill|Ten'ichi Tenjō|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten'ichi Tenjō|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten'ichi Tenjō|qq=}} cycle.
