Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thủy (Ngũ hành)|10=pt|11=Água (astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|lt=Water (水)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=Вода (У-сін)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thủy (Ngũ hành)|10=pt|11=Água (astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|2=uk|3=Вода (У-сін)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thủy (Ngũ hành)|10=pt|11=Água (astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|1=Water (wuxing)|lt=Water (水)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=Вода (У-сін)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thủy (Ngũ hành)|10=pt|11=Água (astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|2=uk|3=Вода (У-сін)|lt=Water (水)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|lt=Water (水)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=Вода (У-сін)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thủy (Ngũ hành)|10=pt|11=Água (astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|2=uk|3=Вода (У-сін)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thủy (Ngũ hành)|10=pt|11=Água (astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water (Wu Xing)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water (Wu Xing)|13=User:Immanuelle/Water (wuxing)|lt=Water (水)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=Вода (У-сін)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thủy (Ngũ hành)|10=pt|11=Água (astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|qq=}}, creating a {{ill|Five Elements#Mutual overcoming|ja|相剋|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Five Elements#Mutual overcoming|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Five Elements#Mutual overcoming|qq=}} (Earth overcomes Water) relationship.
==Pronunciation== * English: Yin Earth Pig (己亥) ** Chinese (Mandarin Pinyin): jǐhài ** Cantonese (Jyutping): gei2 hoi6 ** Japanese: ***Kunyomi 1: Tsuchinoto-i ***Kunyomi 2: Kido-no-inoshishi ***Onyomi 1: kikai ** Korean (Revised Romanization, Hangul): gihae (기해) ** Vietnamese (Hán-Việt): Kỷ Hợi
<!-- == * Yin Earth Pig (己亥) ** Chinese (Mandarin Pinyin): jǐhài ** Cantonese (Jyutping): gei2 hoi6 ** Japanese: ***Kunyomi: つちのといのしし (tsuchinoto-inoshishi) ***Onyomi: きかのいのしし (kika-no-inoshishi) ***Onyomi: きがい (kigai) ** Korean (Revised Romanization): gihae ** Vietnamese (Hán-Việt): Kỷ Hợi
--> ==Years of Yin Earth Pig== Years in which the remainder when divided by 60 is 39 are considered Yin Earth Pig years.
{| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of the Yin Earth Pig''' |- ![[1st millennium]]!![[2nd millennium]]!![[3rd millennium]] |- | * [[39]] * [[99]] * [[159]] * [[219]] * [[279]] * [[339]] * [[399]] * [[459]] * [[519]] * [[579]] * [[639]] * [[699]] * [[759]] * [[819]] * [[879]] * [[939]] * [[999]] | * [[:en:1059|1059]] * [[1119]] * [[1179]] * [[1239]] * [[1299]] * [[1359]] * [[1419]] * [[1479]] * [[1539]] * [[1599]] * [[1659]] * [[1719]] * [[1779]] * [[1839]] * [[1899]] * [[1959]] | * [[2019]] * [[2079]] * [[2139]] * [[2199]] * [[2259]] * [[2319]] * [[2379]] * [[2439]] * [[2499]] * [[2559]] * [[2619]] * [[2679]] * [[2739]] * [[2799]] * [[2859]] * [[2919]] * [[2979]] |}
==Months of Yin Earth Pig== In years where the last digit is 1 or 6 (corresponding to the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stem]] {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|lt=Kanoto (辛)|2=ja|3=辛|4=zh|5=辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|lt=Hinoe (丙)|2=ja|3=丙|4=zh|5=丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=}}), the [[:en:October|October]] of that year is considered a Yin Earth Pig month. However, this applies to the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}, and in some cases, the [[:en:Solar term|Solar term]] (from [[:en:Lidong|Lidong]] to the day before [[:en:Daxue (solar term)|Daxue]]) is used.
==Days of Yin Earth Pig== === Selection Days === Yin Earth Pig days are the 7th day of the {{ill|Ten'ichi Tenjō|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten'ichi Tenjō|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten'ichi Tenjō|qq=}} cycle.
