{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Earth Pig|kanji=己亥|romaji=tsuchinoto i|onyomi=kigai|p=jǐhài|w=chi-hai|mi=t͡ɕi³⁵ xaɪ̯|y=gei2 hoi6|j=gei2 hoi6|ci=kei hɐi|mc=kɨj ɣəi|oc-bs=kɯʔ ɢəʔ|qq=}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}} '''Yin Earth Pig''', also known as '''Kigai''' (己亥, Tsuchinoto-i, Kidonoinoshishi, Kigai), is one of the elements in the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.
It is the 36th combination in the Sexagenary cycle, following {{ill|Wu Xu|ja|1=Yang Earth Dog|2=ja|戊戌|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wu Xu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wu Xu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Earth Dog|qq=}} and preceding {{ill|Geng Zi|ja|1=Yang Metal Rat|2=ja|庚子|1=Yang Metal Rat|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Geng Zi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Geng Zi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Metal Rat|qq=}}. According to {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stem]] {{ill|Ji|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|lt=Tsuchinoto (己)|2=ja|3=己|4=zh|5=己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ji|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ji|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Earth (Wu Xing)|ja|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|zh|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|lt=Earth (土)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|zh|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля